-- New York Capital District REMSCO protocols
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'CD-1001', 'Cardiac Arrest - Adult', 'Cardiac', 'High-quality CPR. Defibrillate VF/VT. Epinephrine 1mg IV/IO q3-5min. Amiodarone 300mg then 150mg. Consider sodium bicarbonate, calcium, magnesium for specific indications.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Capital District REMSCO - Albany Schenectady Rensselaer Saratoga' AND c.state = 'New York' LIMIT 1;
